channel.itunes:summary:
Real estate video tours of homes in the Annapolis Maryland region presented by Liz Wojcicki of Prudential Carruthers Realtors.
I have been a Realtor since 1986 and a long time Annapolitan enjoying everything the "Land of Pleasant Living" has to offer. I work with a wide variety of clients from first time buyers to empty nesters downsizing. Real Estate isn't just "business" to me, it's personal. The sale of a home is often an intricate and emotional transaction for the buyer and seller. It is beneficial to work with an experienced agent who can calmly and knowledgeably guide you past the landmines. I look forward to being of service. P.S. It's pronounced "Whoa Chick ee" Fun to say, Easy to work with!
For more information, contact Liz Wojcicki or by phone at 410-266-0600, by email at liz@mris.com, or visit her website online at www.liz.wojcicki.pcragent.com today.
